metadata.plot: The process of excavating an ominous grave unleashes dreadful consequences buried underneath.
metadata.overview: After tracing the origin of a disturbing supernatural affliction to a wealthy family's ancestral gravesite, a team of paranormal experts relocates the remains—and soon discovers what happens to those who dare to mess with the wrong grave.
metadata.title: Exhuma

release_dates.note: Club Imagine @ Imagine Fantastic Film Festival
